    "The nodes of the network are individual books, while the edges represent reused sentences between two books.",
    "The total count of text reuse for each book in the selected collection is displayed above.",
    "By clicking the corresponding edges, users can explore reused sentences between any two books.",
    "At the chapter level, the platform displays the text reuse distribution of a target book using a rectangular tree diagram.",
